#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Sāmaññavagga "
msgstr "5. Similarity "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Sandiṭṭhikanibbānasutta "
msgstr "47. Extinguishment Is Visible in This Very Life "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an9.47:1.1"
msgid "“‘Sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānan’ti, āvuso, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend, they say that ‘extinguishment is visible in this very life’. "

msgctxt "an9.47:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "In what way did the Buddha say extinguishment is visible in this very life?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an9.47:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāvuso, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "“First, take a mendicant who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures … enters and remains in the first absorption. "

msgctxt "an9.47:2.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā pariyāyena … pe …. "
msgstr "To this extent the Buddha said that extinguishment is visible in this very life in a qualified sense. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an9.47:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā parikkhīṇā honti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements come to an end. "

msgctxt "an9.47:3.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, sandiṭṭhikaṃ nibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā nippariyāyenā”ti. "
msgstr "To this extent the Buddha said that extinguishment is visible in this very life in a definitive sense.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.47:3.3"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

